attributes.title: ViaHost, Sryden, ExoHost, AltHost, HelioNodes, BlockNode | Bad/Layer

attributes.contentHtml:
I decided to make a thread about this new hosting, because I think it's very suspicous.

First of all, they were reselling FalixNodes' servers many times (according to this thread: https://winterhoax.com/d/109-viahost) and now they decided to start a real minecraft hosting.

First thing that is suspicous that they don't pay anything at all for the nodes.
(According to the owner, the nodes are from a provider called "ArvanCloud")

Second thing that there is no TOS and Privacy Policies at all. Not even on the page, or on the discord.

Nothing on the main page btw, no information about the hosting.

Here are the hosting types that they provide
(when they opened there was an option called discord bot hosting but they removed that because they didn't find a ptero egg)

One thing to mention: my vanilla server with no plugins on this hosting took more than a minute to start lol "Can't keep up! Is the server overloaded? Running 5023ms or 100 ticks behind"

They give 6GB ram and 115% cpu core (they keep changing it so it might be different when you read this thread) for free, the #nodes channel in the discord has lack of information.

Great rules too:

The #information channel in Discord is fully empty:

Another thing to mention that the owner is 14

Personally I don't think that this hosting is ready for opening, website is not set up, discord is not set up, missing ptero eggs, slow nodes, etc.
forgot to say, the panel's domain is panel.viahost.ml and the website's domain is viahost.gq (why two different domains?)
leastile does it matter?
leastile I love freenom hosts!
leastile Cause they dont know about cloudfare!
@leastile Hmmmmmm. Yeah, Olliwes told me about this guy too.
This guy doesn't have money to pay for nodes, no tos or privacy policy or anything, kid without money running a host

AYS just because De1 is donated doesnt mean that I dont have money
in fact I have 120+ but im not ready to invest into the hosting yet
AYS He is also using free websites
AYS He is probbably on a gcp free trial N1 server

no
we are just new
ill setup shit tmrw k?

Yeah def not the best host
i mean yea we dont have a client panel
big question, why would you accept a random vps from a random person?
leastile btw the guy isn't a random person and by the way don't involve me in this I just got executive because I am his friend.
deleting random servers?
leastile how do you "accidentally" delete a server there's a confirm window in ptero
kinda sus mate
LMFAOO
J0SH oh
He's one of my friends which is what ThatBad doesn't know. He is not random
true tho
leastile I fixed that issue today
ngl I had to install ptero for him because he couldn't do it himself, which explains him accidentally deleting a server since he is new to ptero admin lmao

And they don't pay anything for their nodes because they have literally only just started about 2 hours ago. I finished their pterodactyl install 2 hours ago and they've already been winterhoaxed, not that fair to me.
